commands.name: NOP
commands.short_desc: Has no effect and is commonly used to pad CLEO scripts with extra space to avoid the jump-at-zero-offset bug

commands.name: WAIT
commands.short_desc: Pauses the script execution for specified amount of time in milliseconds

commands.name: GOTO
commands.short_desc: Transfers the script execution to the label unconditionally

commands.name: SHAKE_CAM
commands.short_desc: Shakes the camera with the given intensity

commands.name: SET_VAR_INT
commands.short_desc: Sets the integer value of the VAR

commands.name: SET_VAR_FLOAT
commands.short_desc: Sets the float value of the VAR

commands.name: SET_VAR_TEXT_LABEL
commands.short_desc: Stores a short string into a variable

commands.name: GOTO_IF_TRUE
commands.short_desc: Transfers the script execution to the label if the condition result is true

commands.name: GOTO_IF_FALSE
commands.short_desc: Transfers the script execution to the label if the condition result is false

commands.name: TERMINATE_THIS_SCRIPT
commands.short_desc: Ends the current script, preventing further execution

commands.name: START_NEW_SCRIPT
commands.short_desc: Starts a new script at the specified label

commands.name: GOSUB
commands.short_desc: Transfers the script execution to the label as a subroutine

commands.name: RETURN
commands.short_desc: Returns from the current subroutine (0025) or function (037A, 037B)

commands.name: CREATE_PLAYER
commands.short_desc: Creates a player at the specified location

commands.name: ADD_TIMED_VAL_TO_FLOAT_VAR
commands.short_desc: Multiplies the delta time since the last frame by the specified value and adds the result to the specified variable

commands.name: ADD_TIMED_FLOAT_VAR_TO_FLOAT_VAR
commands.short_desc: Multiplies the delta time since the last frame by the float value of the variable and adds the result to another variable

commands.name: SUB_TIMED_VAL_FROM_FLOAT_VAR
commands.short_desc: Multiplies the delta time since the last frame by the specified float value and subtracts the result from the specified variable

commands.name: SUB_TIMED_FLOAT_VAR_FROM_FLOAT_VAR
commands.short_desc: Multiplies the delta time since the last frame by the value of the specified variable and subtracts the result from the specified variable

commands.name: CSET_VAR_INT_TO_VAR_FLOAT
commands.short_desc: Converts the float in the second variable to an integer (via flooring) and stores the result into the first variable

commands.name: CSET_VAR_FLOAT_TO_VAR_INT
commands.short_desc: Converts the integer value of the second variable to a float and stores the result in the first variable

commands.name: ABS_INT
commands.short_desc: Returns the absolute value of the integer variable

commands.name: ABS_FLOAT
commands.short_desc: Returns the absolute value of the float variable

commands.name: GENERATE_RANDOM_FLOAT
commands.short_desc: Returns a random float between 0.0 to 1.0

commands.name: GENERATE_RANDOM_INT
commands.short_desc: Returns a random integer between 0 and 65535

commands.name: CREATE_CHAR

commands.name: DELETE_CHAR
commands.short_desc: Removes the character from the game and mission cleanup list, freeing game memory

commands.name: CHAR_WANDER_DIR
commands.short_desc: Sets the character's wander direction

commands.name: CHAR_FOLLOW_PATH
commands.short_desc: Sets the character's follow path

commands.name: CHAR_SET_IDLE
commands.short_desc: Sets the character's objective to stay idle

commands.name: GET_CHAR_COORDINATES
commands.short_desc: Returns the character's coordinates

commands.name: SET_CHAR_COORDINATES
commands.short_desc: Puts the character at the specified location

commands.name: IS_CHAR_STILL_ALIVE
commands.short_desc: Returns true if the handle is a valid character handle who is still alive

commands.name: IS_CHAR_IN_AREA_2D
commands.short_desc: Returns true if the character is within the specified 2D area

commands.name: IS_CHAR_IN_AREA_3D
commands.short_desc: Returns true if the character is within the specified 3D area

commands.name: PRINT_SOON

commands.name: RETURN_FALSE
